    "content": {
        "rendered": "<h2>Basic Setup</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new Field Group</li>\n<li>Add a Flexible Content field</li>\n<li>Configure layouts:\n<ul>\n<li>Create layout types</li>\n<li>Add fields to each layout</li>\n<li>Set minimum/maximum</li>\n<li>Configure button labels</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Common Use Cases</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Page Building\n<ul>\n<li>Content sections</li>\n<li>Landing pages</li>\n<li>Dynamic layouts</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Content Management\n<ul>\n<li>Article components</li>\n<li>Product displays</li>\n<li>Feature blocks</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Plan layouts carefully</li>\n<li>Use clear layout labels</li>\n<li>Consider nesting depth</li>\n<li>Optimize for editors</li>\n</ul>\n",
